*《[[大棋盤|大國政治——全球戰略大思考]]》，台北，立緒文化出版<ref>{{Cite web|title=大國政治：全球戰略大思考|url=http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010385388|accessdate=2020-10-04|work=博客來|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629080218/https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010385388|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=CP1897.com {{!}} 商務印書館門市網站|url=http://www.cp1897.com.hk/product_info.php?BookId=9789867416797|accessdate=2020-10-04|work=www.cp1897.com.hk|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220100033/http://www.cp1897.com.hk/product_info.php?BookId=9789867416797|dead-url=no}}</ref>
